*Stashing =  is process of taking and saving the dirty state (modified tracked files and staged changes) of the repository for later 
	     re-use later. This dirty state can be applied from within another branch.


---------

*Save the dirty state :

git stash

*OR

git stash save <custom_stash_name>

* Only tracked files will saved by the stash 

---------

*Display the list of stashes :

git stash list

----------

*Remove/Delete a stash :

git stash drop <stash_name>

----------

*Show saved stash details :

git stash show <stash_name> 

   
